# Sintaura integration-test configuration
#
# Used by {Entity}ProviderIntegrationTest to call a real Dataverse environment.
# Resolution order (first non-blank wins):
#   1. -D system properties      : -Ddataverse.baseUrl=... -Ddataverse.accessToken=...
#   2. environment variables     : DATAVERSE_BASE_URL, DATAVERSE_ACCESS_TOKEN
#   3. this file (uncomment below)
#
# When neither baseUrl nor accessToken is provided, the integration test is
# silently skipped via JUnit Assumptions — the build stays green.
#
# Example:
# dataverse.baseUrl=https://orgXXXXXXXX.crm4.dynamics.com
# dataverse.accessToken=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOi...

dataverse.baseUrl=
dataverse.accessToken=
